race.comment: Former NSW galloper FLORAL LEGEND (4) is unlucky to still be a maiden finishing runner-up at her past three outings and should find this easier than what she faced down south. Strikes a winnable contest here and rates the testing material. DAITANNA (1) will strip fitter second-up from the spell and again gets the services of Maloney to navigate from the sticky draw. Watch for sharp improvement. QUEEN ARNI (6) has placed at her past three starts over this track and trip and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Top-three credentials. GOLDARNIE (9) has placed two of three over this sprint journey and may earn some minor money again. WINNING FLAME (13) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown some ability at the trials and any market support must be noted.
